contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|quatro}} '''Quatro''' may refer to: *[[Cuatro (instrument)]] (or Quatro), a musical instrument *''[[Éramos Quatro]]'', the seventh album of the Brazilian rock band Raimundos *[[Lego Quatro]], a Lego theme designed for very young children *[[Mike Quatro]], musician and independent entertainment executive *[[Nvidia Quadro]], a model of video card by nVidia *[[Quatro (album)|''Quatro'' (album)]], a 1974 album by Suzi Quatro *[[Quatro (beverage)]], a soft drink *[[Quatro Ciàcoe]], a monthly periodical in Venetian language, established in 1981 *[[Suzi Quatro]] (born 1950), major rock star, actor, and radio researcher/presenter *[[Suzi Quatro (album)|''Suzi Quatro'' (album)]], Suzi Quatro's 1973 debut album ==See also== *[[Cuatro (disambiguation)]] *[[Quattro (disambiguation)]] *[[Quarto (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation}}
